| Modelo          | PrecisiÃ³n Clase 1 | Recall Clase 1 | F1-score Clase 1 | Exactitud |
|----------------|-------------------|----------------|------------------|-----------|
| SVM            | â­ Alta            | â­ Alta        | â­ Alta           | >92%      |
| Random Forest  | Alta              | Alta           | Alta             | >87%      |
| Ãrbol DecisiÃ³n | Media             | Media          | Media            | >82%      |

